{"tid":1702411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會選舉係我地揸政府春袋，搞清楚主次","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:21:44.000Z","uid":86270,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5428013516b5c7b4507227962e452f593718e505","tid":1702411,"uid":86270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"頭先個po嬲得濟講唔清，令人覺得我叫大家唔好投票，我錯<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉係一套政府定落黎嘅遊戲規則，要搞清楚，係個政府要驚我地唔係佢個rule下面玩，而唔係我地盲目相信區議會<br />\n<br />\n上一個po嘅巴打屌得我啱，嬴得幾多得幾多，我同意，但唔好求個政府俾個選舉我地<br />\n建制呢幾日係咁放風取消區議會選舉，佢唔選咪攬炒囉，唔洗求個政府架<br />\n<br />\n總之有得選就選，政府威脅我地就唔好妥協求個政府，呢個就係我想表達嘅野<br />\n<br />\n如果前一個po有表達唔清楚嘅野，我向大家道歉，我係戇鳩衝動累事嘅仆街"},{"pid":"14ec4988bb2f73d9c5c444aec8c1661536322d5b","tid":1702411,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"b56990d63d0f9d5a5e53a4b4d93d6a7f4119ac4d","tid":1702411,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"區選成績 半數議席都贏唔到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724079</a>"},{"pid":"f0bf7c1dfbc8fda73340d66cb1f175909db73765","tid":1702411,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n黎明早起，癱瘓交通，三罷全塞！繼續攬佢老母炒！</span></span></strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6eDeAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6eDeAT.jpg&h=65c50f3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58084e4cd66a7e7ba689d301fb193c61f6117d10","tid":1702411,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"點唔在乎區選都一定要照投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}